code: public Tuple7Builder<T0, T1, T2, T3, T4, T5, T6> add(T0 value0, T1 value1, T2 value2, T3 value3, T4 value4, T5 value5, T6 value6) {     tuples.add(new Tuple7<>(value0, value1, value2, value3, value4, value5, value6)).     return this. }
@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") public Tuple7<T0, T1, T2, T3, T4, T5, T6>[] build() {     return tuples.toArray(new Tuple7[tuples.size()]). }
